# Customer Feedback Intelligence Platform

A production-quality NLP pipeline that fine-tunes transformer models on real customer reviews, builds a RAG retrieval system, generates automated insights using LLMs, and presents everything in an interactive dashboard.

Built as a portfolio project targeting **NLP Engineer** and **AI Data Scientist** roles.

---

