## Project Structure

```
customer-feedback-intelligence/
в”ңв”Җв”Җ config.yaml          вҶҗ All hyperparameters (no hardcoded values in code)
в”ңв”Җв”Җ requirements.txt
в”ңв”Җв”Җ README.md
в”ңв”Җв”Җ run_stage1.py        вҶҗ Stage 1 runner
в”ңв”Җв”Җ data/
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ raw/             вҶҗ Per-category cached parquet (auto-generated)
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ processed/       вҶҗ train/val/test splits + stats
в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ evaluation/      вҶҗ Validation reports + eval results
в”ңв”Җв”Җ models/
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ sentiment/       вҶҗ DistilBERT + LoRA weights
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ aspect/          вҶҗ RoBERTa + LoRA weights
в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ embeddings/      вҶҗ FAISS index + ChromaDB
в”ңв”Җв”Җ notebooks/
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ 01_data_exploration.ipynb
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ 02_model_training.ipynb
в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ 03_evaluation.ipynb
в”ңв”Җв”Җ src/
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ utils.py         вҶҗ Config, logger, seed, device
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ data/
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ loader.py         вҶҗ HuggingFace download + splitting
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ preprocessor.py   вҶҗ Text cleaning + validation
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ dataloader.py     вҶҗ PyTorch Dataset + DataLoader
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ visualise.py      вҶҗ Stats plots
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ models/
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ sentiment.py      вҶҗ DistilBERT + LoRA fine-tuning
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ aspect.py         вҶҗ RoBERTa + LoRA fine-tuning
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ topics.py         вҶҗ BERTopic
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ retrieval/
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ embeddings.py     вҶҗ Embedding generation + indexing
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ search.py         вҶҗ FAISS + ChromaDB search
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ reranker.py       вҶҗ Cross-encoder reranking
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ insights/
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ summariser.py     вҶҗ Cluster summarisation
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ trends.py         вҶҗ Trend detection
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ reports.py        вҶҗ Weekly report generation
в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ evaluation/
в”Ӯ       в”ңв”Җв”Җ metrics.py        вҶҗ All eval metrics
в”Ӯ       в””в”Җв”Җ regression.py     вҶҗ Regression testing
в””в”Җв”Җ dashboard/
    в”ңв”Җв”Җ app.py
    в””в”Җв”Җ pages/
        в”ңв”Җв”Җ overview.py
        в”ңв”Җв”Җ search.py
        в”ңв”Җв”Җ topics.py
        в”ңв”Җв”Җ insights.py
        в””в”Җв”Җ performance.py
```

---

## Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|-----------|
| Core ML | PyTorch 2.2, Transformers 4.40 |
| Fine-tuning | PEFT/LoRA (parameter-efficient) |
| Embeddings | sentence-transformers (all-MiniLM-L6-v2) |
| Topic modelling | BERTopic |
| Vector search | FAISS + ChromaDB |
| LLM | Groq API вҖ” Llama 3 8B |
| Evaluation | scikit-learn metrics |
| Dashboard | Streamlit |
| Data | HuggingFace datasets |

---

## Hardware

Designed for **CPU / Apple Silicon (MPS)** вҖ” no GPU required.

Device auto-detection order: CUDA вҶ’ MPS вҶ’ CPU.

LoRA reduces trainable parameters to ~1% of full model, making training feasible on a standard laptop.

